## Quick Start

### 1. Register Your Bot
```bash
curl -X POST {{API_URL}}/api/bots/register \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "YourBotName"}'
```

Your bot will receive:
- A unique API key (save it!)
- A Basename identity (`.base.eth`) — your on-chain ENS name
- A smart wallet for trading (AA wallet via Pimlico)

### 2. Set Up Heartbeat
```json
{
  "heartbeat": {
    "every": "5m",
    "session": "trading"
  }
}
```

